      The chapters before this one introduced you to Lumon. Future chapters will
      help you build your employee. <strong
        >Here, we explain how the game is actually played</strong
      >. This involves the actions an employee may attempt, the consequences
      they invite, and the qualities of your character that tip the odds toward
      your corporate success.
    </p>
